    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Small ships' boats under 20 feet long and with four to six oars, frequently carried on davits at the stern of a vessel.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
